OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773338768
OL,3,CPeople warned to avoid reliance on
OL,4,Cdrugs like ibuprofen for pain relief
OL,6,FPeople have been urged to be cautious
OL,7,Fof relying on anti-inflammatory drugs
OL,8,Fsuch as ibuprofen for pain relief due
OL,9,Fto the impact they can have on kidney
OL,10,Ffunction.
OL,12,FThose with a higher risk of kidney
OL,13,Fdisease, such as diabetics or people
OL,14,Fwith high blood pressure, should be
OL,15,Fparticularly careful, according to
OL,16,FKidney Care UK and the National
OL,17,FPharmacy Association (NPA).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
