OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773338768
OL,3,CPeople warned to avoid reliance on
OL,4,Cdrugs like ibuprofen for pain relief
OL,6,FNon-steroidal anti-inflammatory drugs
OL,7,F(NSAIDs) such as ibuprofen, naproxen
OL,8,Fand diclofenac can increase blood
OL,9,Fpressure and damage blood vessels
OL,10,Finside the kidneys.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FOlivier Picard, chair of the NPA, said
OL,18,Fthat medicines "have the power to harm
OL,19,Fas well as to heal".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
