OL,3,CPeople warned to avoid reliance on
OL,4,Cdrugs like ibuprofen for pain relief
OL,6,FKidney Care UK also estimates that
OL,7,Fabout one million people are
OL,8,Fundiagnosed.
OL,10,FThose at an increased risk of
OL,11,Fdeveloping the condition include:
OL,12,Fdiabetics; people with high blood
OL,13,Fpressure; people with a family history
OL,14,Fof kidney disease; and those from
OL,15,Fblack and south Asian communities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
