OL,3,CPeople warned to avoid reliance on
OL,4,Cdrugs like ibuprofen for pain relief
OL,6,FFiona Loud, policy director at Kidney
OL,7,FCare UK, said: "Kidney disease can
OL,8,Fhappen to anyone at any time, and can
OL,9,Fhave a devastating impact on your
OL,10,Flife, relationships, finances as well
OL,11,Fas your physical and mental health."
OL,13,FOf the 294,999 people who completed
OL,14,Fthe charity's kidney health checker
OL,15,Fbetween October 2024 and March 2026,
OL,16,Falmost a quarter (24%) said they
OL,17,Fregularly used over-the-counter
OL,18,Fmedication for pain relief.
OL,26,@oD@POUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
