PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773338768
OL,3,CPeople warned to avoid reliance on
OL,4,Cdrugs like ibuprofen for pain relief
OL,6,F"You can lose up to 90% of your kidney
OL,7,Ffunction without realising, so it's
OL,8,Fimportant to be aware of the signs to
OL,9,Flook out for, to know if you might be
OL,10,Fat increased risk, and what to do if
OL,11,Fyou are concerned," Ms Loud said. "It
OL,12,Fonly takes a few minutes to complete
OL,13,Four online kidney health checker to
OL,14,Fsee if you might be at increased risk.
OL,16,F"If you have any concerns, you can
OL,17,Fraise these with your GP or have a
OL,18,Fchat with your local pharmacist."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@cOUxD@AOUzD@aO]
